<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('./partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet"  href="/public/styles/home.css">
    <title>ServiTrack</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/nav') %>

    <!-- Carousel Section -->
    <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="../public/images/sliderImage1.png" alt="First slide">
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="../public/images/sliderImage2.png" alt="Second slide">
            </div> -->
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What We Offer Section -->
    <section id="what-we-offer" class="what-we-offer-section">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h2>What We Offer</h2>
            <p>At ServiTrack, we specialize in providing top-notch vehicle services to keep your car running smoothly. From oil changes to repairs, we help you manage your vehicle maintenance needs with ease. Book a service, set reminders, and stay on top of your vehicle’s health all in one place.</p>
            
            <div class="service-container">
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h4>Oil Change</h4>
                    <p>Keep your engine running smoothly with regular oil changes. We offer fast and reliable oil change services to ensure your vehicle’s longevity.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h4>Repairs</h4>
                    <p>Whether it’s a mechanical issue or an electrical fault, our expert technicians can handle all types of vehicle repairs to get you back on the road quickly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h4>Service Reminders</h4>
                    <p>Never miss an important service again. Set reminders for routine maintenance, ensuring your vehicle stays in peak condition year-round.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h4>Vehicle Diagnostics</h4>
                    <p>Get your vehicle fully diagnosed to detect any potential issues early. We provide comprehensive diagnostics to ensure optimal performance.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials-section">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>
            <div class="testimonial-container">
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                    <p>"ServiTrack has completely streamlined our vehicle service management. It's so easy to track and schedule services. Highly recommended!"</p>
                    <h5>- Rohit, Fleet Manager</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                    <p>"The real-time tracking feature has been a game-changer for us. We can track every vehicle's service status, ensuring everything runs smoothly."</p>
                    <h5>- Priya , Operations Manager</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                    <p>"I appreciate the reminder system! ServiTrack makes it so much easier to keep track of regular maintenance for our vehicles."</p>
                    <h5>- Vikram , Car Owner</h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section id="about-us" class="about-us-section">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>ServiTrack is dedicated to transforming vehicle maintenance and service management. We provide a seamless platform that allows users to easily book, track, and manage their vehicle services, from routine maintenance to urgent repairs.</p>
            <p>With real-time tracking and reminders for upcoming services, our goal is to ensure that every vehicle stays in top condition, helping our customers save time and keep their vehicles safe on the road.</p>
            <p>Our team is passionate about simplifying vehicle care, giving you the tools to stay in control of all your service needs with ease.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    

    <!-- Contact Us Section -->
    <section id="contact-us" class="contact-us-section">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or would like to learn more about our services, feel free to get in touch with us. We’re here to help!</p>
            <form action="/contact/submit-contact-form" method="post"   >
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
                <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
            </form>
          
        </div>
        
    </section>

  
    
    

    <%- include('./partials/script') %>
</body>
</html>
